\ ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
\ Detect tiles under rectangle
\ ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

|| 0 value a
|| 0 value lx
|| 0 value ly
|| 0 value lw
|| 0 value lh
|| 0 value lx2
|| 0 value ly2
|| 0 value xt

|| : pen-colrow  at@ gap dup 2/ ;

continuation: tread> ( x y w h a - code ; ) ( pen=xy a - )
     to xt  to a  to lh to lw to ly to lx 
     x @ .> lx + dup to lx  lw + 1 - to lx2 
     y @ .> ly + dup to ly  lh + 1 - to ly2
     ly2 gap + ly do
        lx2 gap + lx do
            i lx2 min j ly2 min at  pen-colrow a spot xt execute
            me free? if unloop unloop exit then
        gap +loop
     gap +loop ;
